s=\"crayon-e\">add_header <\/span><span class=\"crayon-v\">Cache<\/span><span class=\"crayon-o\">-<\/span><span class=\"crayon-i\">Control<\/span><span class=\"crayon-h\"> <\/span><span class=\"crayon-s\">\"public\"<\/span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">;<\/span><\/div><div class=\"crayon-line\" id=\"crayon-5c0345a171b79464914204-7\"><span class=\"crayon-h\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"crayon-v\">add<\/span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">_<\/span>header<span class=\"crayon-h\"> <\/span><span class=\"crayon-v\">X<\/span><span class=\"crayon-o\">-<\/span><span class=\"crayon-v\">Frame<\/span><span class=\"crayon-o\">-<\/span><span class=\"crayon-i\">Options<\/span><span class=\"crayon-h\"> <\/span><span class=\"crayon-s\">\"SAMEORIGIN\"<\/span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">;<\/span><\/div><div class=\"crayon-line crayon-striped-line\" id=\"crayon-5c0345a171b79464914204-8\"><span class=\"crayon-h\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<\/span><span class=\"crayon-v\">expires<\/span><span class=\"crayon-h\"> <\/span><span class=\"crayon-o\">+<\/span><span class=\"crayon-cn\">1y<\/span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">;<\/span><\/div><\/div><\/td>\r\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/tr>\r\n\t\t\t\t<\/table>\r\n\t\t\t<\/div>\r\n\t\t<\/div>\r\n<!-- [Format Time: 0.0008 seconds] -->\r\n\n<\/li>\n<li>By default \r\n\t\t\t<span id=\"crayon-5c0345a171b7c795228969\" class=\"crayon-syntax crayon-syntax-inline  crayon-theme-github crayon-theme-github-inline crayon-font-droid-sans-mono\" style=\"font-size: 14px !important; line-height: 20px !important;font-size: 14px !important;\"><span class=\"crayon-pre crayon-code\" style=\"font-size: 14px !important; line-height: 20px !important;font-size: 14px !important; -moz-tab-size:4; -o-tab-size:4; -webkit-tab-size:4; tab-size:4;\"><span class=\"crayon-v\">ico<\/span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">,<\/span><span class=\"crayon-h\"> <\/span><span class=\"crayon-v\">jpg<\/span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">,<\/span><span class=\"crayon-h\"> <\/span><span class=\"crayon-v\">jpeg<\/span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">.<\/span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">.<\/span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">.<\/span><\/span><\/span> files from pub \r\n\t\t\t<span id=\"crayon-5c0345a171b7f298336116\" class=\"crayon-syntax crayon-syntax-inline  crayon-theme-github crayon-theme-github-inline crayon-font-droid-sans-mono\" style=\"font-size: 14px !important; line-height: 20px !important;font-size: 14px !important;\"><span class=\"crayon-pre crayon-code\" style=\"font-size: 14px !important; line-height: 20px !important;font-size: 14px !important; -moz-tab-size:4; -o-tab-size:4; -webkit-tab-size:4; tab-size:4;\"><span class=\"crayon-o\">\/<\/span><span class=\"crayon-m\">static<\/span><\/span><\/span>  expiries after one year.<br \/>\nLet&#8217;s add some conditions to disable caching for stores with developer mode defined on nginx level or simply set \r\n\t\t\t<span id=\"crayon-5c0345a171b83746796665\" class=\"crayon-syntax crayon-syntax-inline  crayon-theme-github crayon-theme-github-inline crayon-font-droid-sans-mono\" style=\"font-size: 14px !important; line-height: 20px !important;font-size: 14px !important;\"><span class=\"crayon-pre crayon-code\" style=\"font-size: 14px !important; line-height: 20px !important;font-size: 14px !important; -moz-tab-size:4; -o-tab-size:4; -webkit-tab-size:4; tab-size:4;\"><span class=\"crayon-e\">expires <\/span><span class=\"crayon-v\">off<\/span><span class=\"crayon-sy\">;<\/span><\/span><\/span> without any conditions.<br \/>\n<!-- Crayon Syntax Highlighter v_2.7.2_beta -->\r\n\r\n\t\t<div id=\"crayon-5c0345a171b85176592521\" class=\"crayon-syntax crayon-theme-github crayon-font-droid-sans-mono crayon-os-pc print-yes notranslate\" data-settings=\" minimize scroll-mouseover\" style=\" margin-top: 12px; margin-bottom: 12px; clear: none; font-size: 14px !important; line-height: 20px !important;\">\r\n\t\t\r\n\t\t\t<div class=\"crayon-toolbar\" data-settings=\" mouseover overlay hide delay\" styl